{"id": "test-00232", "text": "CRICKET - LARA ENDURES ANOTHER MISERABLE DAY.", "gold_mentions": [{"start": 10, "end": 14, "ent_type": "PER", "text": "LARA"}]}
{"id": "test-00233", "text": "Robert Galvin", "gold_mentions": [{"start": 0, "end": 13, "ent_type": "PER", "text": "Robert Galvin"}]}
{"id": "test-00234", "text": "MELBOURNE 1996-12-06", "gold_mentions": [{"start": 0, "end": 9, "ent_type": "LOC", "text": "MELBOURNE"}]}
{"id": "test-00235", "text": "Australia gave Brian Lara another reason to be miserable when they beat West Indies by five wickets in the opening World Series limited overs match on Friday.", "gold_mentions": [{"start": 0, "end": 9, "ent_type": "LOC", "text": "Australia"}, {"start": 15, "end": 25, "ent_type": "PER", "text": "Brian Lara"}, {"start": 72, "end": 83, "ent_type": "LOC", "text": "West Indies"}, {"start": 115, "end": 127, "ent_type": "MISC", "text": "World Series"}]}
{"id": "test-00236", "text": "Lara, disciplined for misconduct on Wednesday, was dismissed for five to extend a disappointing run of form on tour.", "gold_mentions": [{"start": 0, "end": 4, "ent_type": "PER", "text": "Lara"}]}
{"id": "test-00237", "text": "Australia, who hold a 2-0 lead in the five-match test series, overhauled West Indies' total of 172 all out with eight balls to spare to end a run of six successive one-day defeats.", "gold_mentions": [{"start": 0, "end": 9, "ent_type": "LOC", "text": "Australia"}, {"start": 73, "end": 84, "ent_type": "LOC", "text": "West Indies"}]}
{"id": "test-00238", "text": "All-rounder Greg Blewett steered his side to a comfortable victory with an unbeaten 57 in 90 balls to the delight of the 42,442 crowd.", "gold_mentions": [{"start": 12, "end": 24, "ent_type": "PER", "text": "Greg Blewett"}]}
{"id": "test-00239", "text": "Man-of-the match Blewett came to the wicket with the total on 70 for two and hit three fours during an untroubled innings lasting 129 minutes.", "gold_mentions": [{"start": 17, "end": 24, "ent_type": "PER", "text": "Blewett"}]}
{"id": "test-00240", "text": "His crucial fifth-wicket partnership with fellow all-rounder Stuart Law, who scored 21, added 71 off 85 balls.", "gold_mentions": [{"start": 61, "end": 71, "ent_type": "PER", "text": "Stuart Law"}]}
{"id": "test-00241", "text": "Lara looked out of touch during his brief stay at the crease before chipping a simple catch to Shane Warne at mid-wicket.", "gold_mentions": [{"start": 0, "end": 4, "ent_type": "PER", "text": "Lara"}, {"start": 95, "end": 106, "ent_type": "PER", "text": "Shane Warne"}]}
{"id": "test-00242", "text": "West Indies tour manager Clive Lloyd has apologised for Lara's behaviour on Tuesday.", "gold_mentions": [{"start": 0, "end": 11, "ent_type": "LOC", "text": "West Indies"}, {"start": 25, "end": 36, "ent_type": "PER", "text": "Clive Lloyd"}, {"start": 56, "end": 60, "ent_type": "PER", "text": "Lara"}]}
{"id": "test-00243", "text": "He (Lara) had told Australia coach Geoff Marsh that wicketkeeper Ian Healy was unwelcome in the visitors' dressing room.", "gold_mentions": [{"start": 4, "end": 8, "ent_type": "PER", "text": "Lara"}, {"start": 19, "end": 28, "ent_type": "LOC", "text": "Australia"}, {"start": 35, "end": 46, "ent_type": "PER", "text": "Geoff Marsh"}, {"start": 65, "end": 74, "ent_type": "PER", "text": "Ian Healy"}]}
{"id": "test-00244", "text": "The Melbourne crowd were clearly angered by the incident, loudly jeering the West Indies vice-captain as he walked to the middle.", "gold_mentions": [{"start": 4, "end": 13, "ent_type": "LOC", "text": "Melbourne"}, {"start": 77, "end": 88, "ent_type": "LOC", "text": "West Indies"}]}
{"id": "test-00245", "text": "It was left to fellow left-hander Shivnarine Chanderpaul to hold the innings together with a gritty 54 despite the handicap of an injured groin.", "gold_mentions": [{"start": 34, "end": 56, "ent_type": "PER", "text": "Shivnarine Chanderpaul"}]}
{"id": "test-00246", "text": "Chanderpaul was forced to rely on a runner for most of his innings after hurting himself as he scurried back to his crease to avoid being run out.", "gold_mentions": [{"start": 0, "end": 11, "ent_type": "PER", "text": "Chanderpaul"}]}
{"id": "test-00247", "text": "Pakistan, who arrive in Australia later this month, are the other team competing in the World Series tournament.", "gold_mentions": [{"start": 0, "end": 8, "ent_type": "LOC", "text": "Pakistan"}, {"start": 24, "end": 33, "ent_type": "LOC", "text": "Australia"}, {"start": 88, "end": 100, "ent_type": "MISC", "text": "World Series"}]}
{"id": "test-00248", "text": "CRICKET - AUSTRALIA V WEST INDIES WORLD SERIES SCOREBOARD.", "gold_mentions": [{"start": 10, "end": 19, "ent_type": "LOC", "text": "AUSTRALIA"}, {"start": 22, "end": 33, "ent_type": "LOC", "text": "WEST INDIES"}, {"start": 34, "end": 46, "ent_type": "MISC", "text": "WORLD SERIES"}]}
